  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>&gt;<a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"sfrpg.class-features\" data-id=\"sobLlAGQkmWcFBFx\" draggable=\"true\"><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i> Magic Hack</a></p>\n        <p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl54_LabelName\">As a standard action, you can spend 1 Resolve Point to fire a single shot from a ranged weapon at a target known to you within range. The shot travels straight to the target, passing through any nonmagical barrier in its way, ignoring hardness and Hit Points (any magical barrier, such as a <em>wall of force</em>, stops the shot). This ability negates cover and concealment modifiers, but otherwise the attack is rolled normally.</span></p>",
